  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to observe the effective and safety in the laparoscopic repair
      of hiatal hernia using biological patch versus plastic.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      observation indicator:

        1. incidence rate of complications,

        2. postoperative hospital stay

        3. readmission rate in 1st month after operation

        4. recurrence rate after operation

        5. hospitalization costs

        6. Self-evaluation of gastroesophageal reflux symptoms and quality of life(QOL) in
           6th-month, 1st-year,2nd-year,3rd-year,4th-year and 5th-year after operation
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
